_:N549d6eb3268e4abb9b88ac29d782c4ea <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sarah Sackman KC MP was appointed Minister of State in the Ministry of Justice on 2 December 2024. She was Solicitor General from the 9 July 2024 to 2 December 2024. She was elected as the MP for Finchley and Golders Green in July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>She was called to the Bar in 2008 and worked as a barrister at Francis Taylor Building and  Matrix Chambers, focusing on public, election, planning, environment and rating law.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
